rComments: Conscientious, hard working, informative. Works to a high standard meticulously. Integrity and sincerity are strengths.

She's great at teaching, but if you miss class you better get the notes from someone cause you're guaranteed bad grades on the quizzes. Don't expect a high grade on the papers. Overall, low class average and kinda sad
